{"tid":1540934,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐樹窿]比個機會手足撐住你，我地一齊撐落去","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T14:18:03.000Z","uid":284879,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45195c63a97f696e7182f75aa147f4b92722597f","tid":1540934,"uid":284879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"的而且確，而家政權、警黑係好仆街，大家生活都好苦。<br />\n<br />\n你身邊d手足都知道，大家都好清楚！！<br />\n<br />\n我求下你地，求求大家<br />\n<br />\n真係情緒黎了、壓力大到撐唔住，頂唔順時<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">比個機會其他手足，一個機會都好</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">比其他手足有機會陪住你，攬住你</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n都頂唔順，休息下，訓個覺，再唔係係到放低你嘅壓力，咁多位手足都願意陪住你，其他手足一定願意等埋你！<br />\n<br />\n記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n我地仲要齊上齊落，約定煲底除罩相見，一個都不能少！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:一個小社工，只望可以係大家頂唔順嘅時候，願意貢獻自己，比你地知道YOU ARE NOT ALONE，有人肯陪住你撐住你！"},{"pid":"62719d502d039c16989cab27bbaa1678f79c079a","tid":1540934,"uid":263814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"「動議」撤回就收貨？907 入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>撤回程序須於10月1日國慶後<br />\n立法會復會<br />\n明顯係想借機過骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以政府之厚顏 <br />\n在美國人權法暫緩和國慶之後再來反口 <br />\n我地一啲都唔意外</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月係機場月，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">九月七再入機場<br />\n一點鐘 機場巴士總站見</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔揸爆春袋，政府都唔會流眼淚</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民旅客look，冇dresscode，拖喼，少量/冇gear，唔嗌口號，搭巴士入機場！<br />\n<br />\n大家見字一人一post幫手傳開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JWvDnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JWvDnu.jpg&h=6ed8b18a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8qsfS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8qsfS.jpg&h=4359c0d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b03bd5e826e19b3db7684fc81ad71e2620525d","tid":1540934,"uid":284879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"推，求下大家"},{"pid":"fd99b0e09da9698a976c7b6210885380322c1a9b","tid":1540934,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"3f10fb97cbff287eb98c486068db1981f2764117","tid":1540934,"uid":284879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"正能量自推"},{"pid":"bf8284fb681071883f1305c5693abf8a7b8c7431","tid":1540934,"uid":284879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"求求"},{"pid":"b343f6b25c564a25f1ba44d6fd6e13eb78130842","tid":1540934,"uid":284879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"72425b38afdceb4ea4ee7d39f7d28c836f04e36e","tid":1540934,"u